---
import ArchiveLayout from '../layouts/ArchiveLayout.astro';
---

<ArchiveLayout title="Max on Marketing — Home">

  <div class="wp-cards">

    <article class="wp-card">
      <div class="wp-card-text">
        <p class="wp-card-date">May 2, 2019</p>
        <h2 class="wp-card-title"><a href="/archive-voice">Smart Speaker, Why Should I Pay Attention To Voice?</a></h2>
        <p class="wp-card-excerpt">Even with its impressive growth and user adoption, is voice technology living up to its hype? Every decade or so, a new wave of technological innovation bridges the gap to mass adoption and changes how we interact with the world through technology...</p>
        <a href="/archive-voice" class="wp-read-more">Read more</a>
      </div>
      <div class="wp-card-thumb">
        <a href="/archive-voice">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512446816042-444d641267d4?w=256&h=256&fit=crop" alt="Smart Speaker" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="wp-card">
      <div class="wp-card-text">
        <p class="wp-card-date">March 28, 2019</p>
        <h2 class="wp-card-title"><a href="/archive-ogilvy">Confessions of the Original Advertising Man</a></h2>
        <p class="wp-card-excerpt">Over half a century later, David Ogilvy's wit and business acumen still has a spot on the required reading list. Considered required reading for all advertising professionals, Confessions of an Advertising Man by David Ogilvy still reads like an advertising 101 manual 60+ years after its publication...</p>
        <a href="/archive-ogilvy" class="wp-read-more">Read more</a>
      </div>
      <div class="wp-card-thumb">
        <a href="/archive-ogilvy">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=256&h=256&fit=crop" alt="Ogilvy" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="wp-card">
      <div class="wp-card-text">
        <p class="wp-card-date">March 7, 2019</p>
        <h2 class="wp-card-title"><a href="/archive-instagram">Is Instagram Marketing Right For Your Business?</a></h2>
        <p class="wp-card-excerpt">5 questions to answer about your business before marketing with Instagram. The idea that a picture is worth a thousand words can be best understood on Instagram. Starting in 2010 as a social picture sharing platform, Instagram has grown to over 800+ million daily active users...</p>
        <a href="/archive-instagram" class="wp-read-more">Read more</a>
      </div>
      <div class="wp-card-thumb">
        <a href="/archive-instagram">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611162617213-7d7a39e9b1d7?w=256&h=256&fit=crop" alt="Instagram" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="wp-card">
      <div class="wp-card-text">
        <p class="wp-card-date">February 5, 2019</p>
        <h2 class="wp-card-title"><a href="/archive-lasagna">How To Make The Best, Simple Lasagna</a></h2>
        <p class="wp-card-excerpt">A Recipe for Lasagna with 4 Simple Ingredients and 8 Easy Steps. When I think of Italian comfort food, I immediately think of lasagna. A staple of Italian cooking and available on just about any restaurant menu that considers itself authentic Italian cuisine...</p>
        <a href="/archive-lasagna" class="wp-read-more">Read more</a>
      </div>
      <div class="wp-card-thumb">
        <a href="/archive-lasagna">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1574894709920-11b28e7367e3?w=256&h=256&fit=crop" alt="Lasagna" />
        </a>
      </div>
    </article>

  </div>

</ArchiveLayout>

<style>
  .wp-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .wp-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .wp-card:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .wp-card-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .wp-card-date {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    color: #999;
    margin-bottom: 0.375rem;
  }

  .wp-card-title {
    font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 0.625rem;
  }

  .wp-card-title a {
    color: #222;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .wp-card-title a:hover {
    color: #0073aa;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .wp-card-excerpt {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .wp-read-more {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #0073aa;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .wp-read-more:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .wp-card-thumb {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 180px;
  }

  .wp-card-thumb a {
    display: block;
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .wp-card-thumb a:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .wp-card-thumb img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 130px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
</style>
